<div class="calcpad-output">
 <h3>Interpolation</h3>
 <h4>Data functions in CalcpadCE</h4>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>f</var>
   <sub>1</sub>
   (
   <var>x</var>
   )  =
   <b>take</b>
   (
   <var>x</var>
   ; 9; 2; -1; 1; 4.5; 6; -4 )
  </span>
  - discrete values (vector)
  <span style="color:CornflowerBlue;">━━━</span>
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>f</var>
   <sub>2</sub>
   (
   <var>x</var>
   )  =
   <b>line</b>
   (
   <var>x</var>
   ; 9; 2; -1; 1; 4.5; 6; -4 )
  </span>
  - linear interpolation
  <span style="color:YellowGreen;">━━━</span>
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>f</var>
   <sub>3</sub>
   (
   <var>x</var>
   )  =
   <b>spline</b>
   (
   <var>x</var>
   ; 9; 2; -1; 1; 4.5; 6; -4 )
  </span>
  - Hermite spline interpolation
  <span style="color:Tomato;">━━━</span>
 </p>
