 <h4>Application - wind load height factors</h4>
 <p>Height above terrain</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>Z</var>
   (
   <var>x</var>
   )  =
   <b>spline</b>
   (
   <var>x</var>
   ; -0.01; 5; 10; 20; 40; 60; 80; 100; 150; 200; 250; 300; 350 )
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>Load for terrain type A</p>
 <p>
